Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.64,0:00:09.95,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,When watching Hayate no Gotoku, make sure to watch at a good distance away from the TV in a well lit room. 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.41,0:00:15.12,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Spring's right around the corner. 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.12,0:00:17.66,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,The third semester flew by, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.66,0:00:20.81,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? It felt like it took forever to me. 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.81,0:00:27.21,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,But the only days you came to school were when we thought Katsura-sensei was quitting and last episode. 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.62,0:00:34.34,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the main heroine, so when the story takes place at Hakuou, I have no choice but to show up. 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.34,0:00:37.23,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,There you go mumbling nonsense again. 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.23,0:00:38.86,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home, Hayate. 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.86,0:00:42.70,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, why is school such a big pain? 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.70,0:00:47.59,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,But then, it'd be a different story if this were Hou**ka Academy or Ku***. 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.59,0:00:51.16,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I would like to try the Ashi**do Academy's uniform once. {people get the names?} 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.70,0:00:54.78,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Milady's hatred of school is really over the top. 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.36,0:01:00.36,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Why, why. Who do we have here? 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.36,0:01:03.62,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,If it isn't Hayata-kun and Nagi-chan. {hay to Kotomi!} 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.62,0:01:05.13,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,What a coincidence. 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.13,0:01:06.86,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,How may I help you all? 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.86,0:01:09.79,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,We thought we'd take part in our club activity for once. {sense is unmaking, are they trying to get hayate and nagi to take part in their (student council trio) club? -Fluff}{Al - actually I think this makes sense in that they're saying they're not skipping club}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.79,0:01:10.96,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Club? 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.96,0:01:14.93,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I always assumed that none of you were involved in any clubs. 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.97,0:01:19.04,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,Are you interested, Hayata-kun? 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.04,0:01:19.80,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,What?! 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.80,0:01:20.73,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,No, not really. 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.73,0:01:24.28,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,What? "I'd love to participate", you said? 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.28,0:01:26.20,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Then stop by our club room. 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.45,0:01:27.80,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,Come, come. 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.79,0:01:31.54,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.15,0:01:33.98,Default,3,0000,0000,0000,,Just as planned. 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.27,0:01:40.77,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Did you all know that there's a huge mansion like this in the middle of Tokyo? 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.77,0:01:42.92,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The name of the mistress who lives there is Sanzenin Nagi. 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.92,0:01:43.72,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,And... 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.85,0:01:48.08,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Her butler's name is Ayasaki Hayate. 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.08,0:01:49.89,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The two are slightly airheaded... 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.89,0:01:52.27,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,...and they misunderstand each other a bit... 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.27,0:01:57.47,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,...but they are bound by a tight master-butler bond. 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.25,0:02:03.13,Default,3,0000,0000,0000,,This story takes place when hu**** were still able to fly. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.58,0:03:39.44,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Motion Picture Research Club? 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.33,0:03:43.72,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,You really have a unique club room. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.72,0:03:46.97,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,The building is made according to the club founder's taste. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.04,0:03:53.50,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,This is a 16mm film! 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:56.54,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,This is a super HARP camera! 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.54,0:03:59.55,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I got it. You're basically a MC! 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:00.82,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,A Movie Club! 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:03.12,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about... 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.12,0:04:04.06,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,...Little bunny? 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.07,0:04:06.26,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't? 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.81,0:04:09.27,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have any intention of shooting movies. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:11.33,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do anything that difficult. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.33,0:04:13.93,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Then what do you do here? 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.54,0:04:15.68,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,That's obvious! 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.87,0:04:22.27,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,We film and gather all sorts of funny movies and laugh at them with everyone! 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.85,0:04:26.11,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we're also called Niko **** Movie Club. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.11,0:04:27.54,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,In short- 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.54,0:04:29.78,Default,3,0000,0000,0000,,You-To-be~ 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.78,0:04:31.49,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,"In short?" 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.49,0:04:34.07,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,So basically a boredom killing club. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.07,0:04:36.24,Default,3,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling the boredom killing club?! 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.18,0:04:36.89,Default-alt,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Motion Picture Research Club, huh? 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.32,0:04:39.82,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds a little interesting. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.66,0:04:45.34,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's this? Milady has an interest in getting involved with people. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.34,0:04:48.20,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,I think she's interested in the motion pictures. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.57,0:04:50.76,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of it, Nagi-chan, are you in any clubs? 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:52.57,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not in any right now. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.57,0:04:54.91,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,Then give this one a try. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.91,0:05:00.12,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,We're a really lax club originally made to take shots of cute girls. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.12,0:05:02.57,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,So it'll work as a way of making memories. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.10,0:05:05.48,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do... 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:07.05,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,This is a chance. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.51,0:05:12.59,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,It's a great opportunity for Milady, who tends to be a hikikomori, to enjoy regular school life. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.22,0:05:15.69,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Who would ever call me a butler if I don't support her being in it?! 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.22,0:05:17.20,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.20,0:05:19.94,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it sounds very interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.94,0:05:24.09,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,So, what kind of footage do you actually shoot? 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:27.82,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,The works are lying around there. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.57,0:05:30.62,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Then let me see some. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.43,0:05:38.38,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,You said you shoot footage of cute girls, right? 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.01,0:05:43.52,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, I'm Ayasaki Hayako. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.52,0:05:45.39,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,A little mischievous sixteen year old. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.83,0:05:49.93,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,Some nice-looking men out there take me out on dates! 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.61,0:05:54.82,Default,3,0000,0000,0000,,No! There goes our work! 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.82,0:05:56.43,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,What was that spy shot about?! 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.43,0:05:57.91,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,You even dubbed over it! 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.91,0:05:59.62,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? It's funny. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.62,0:06:02.32,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, cameras are set everywhere. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:06.73,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,From the pinnacle of Chomolungma to Shi**ka-chan's shower room over at Minamoto-san's. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.92,0:06:11.30,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,No, you can't film! Stop! 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.30,0:06:13.28,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about this? 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.80,0:06:22.14,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei! I... I can't hold myself back anymore! 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.14,0:06:27.12,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You can't, Ayasaki-kun. We're student and teacher. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.12,0:06:30.73,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to stay like this with you. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.73,0:06:33.64,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,You fool. Don't trouble me like that. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:35.60,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Being able to cheat is a sign that a guy's dependable. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.60,0:06:37.65,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Girls are around for you. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.11,0:06:46.86,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,You're making me look like the biggest flirt in the world! 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.37,0:06:51.05,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hayate. What was all of that about? 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.05,0:06:54.73,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Th-They're accidents! They were all purely accidents! 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.26,0:06:56.22,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Milady. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.95,0:06:59.89,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take our leave now. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:02.52,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're going to leave, Hayata-kun? 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:04.27,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,You just got here. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.27,0:07:07.97,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to see any other sketchy footage. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.55,0:07:11.49,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:14.10,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Please, help us. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:16.61,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Help? What do you mean? 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:22.32,Default,Kuz,0000,0000,0000,,You all seem to be having fun. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.48,0:07:23.44,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Superintendent! 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.44,0:07:24.89,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What brings you here? 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.57,0:07:29.71,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Today's club investigation day run personally by Kuzuha-sama! 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.31,0:07:31.53,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Investigation? 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.79,0:07:35.45,Default,Kuz,0000,0000,0000,,I'm checking to make sure nothing has strayed from what students should be doing. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.45,0:07:36.73,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.53,0:07:41.63,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,So she does some normal stuff once in a while. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.63,0:07:43.54,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be deceived, Hayata-kun. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.88,0:07:48.14,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,How could she be normal? 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.14,0:07:52.58,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any clue how much suffering stems from her investigations? 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.58,0:07:54.05,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,For example, in the Tennis Club. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.93,0:07:58.06,Default,Kuz,0000,0000,0000,,No one can hit a Boomerang S***e here? 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.06,0:07:58.96,Default,Kuz,0000,0000,0000,,Closed down. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.95,0:08:02.29,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,In the American Football Club- 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.85,0:08:06.64,Default,Kuz,0000,0000,0000,,They can't even do a ***bat Dive in midair? 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.64,0:08:07.65,Default,Kuz,0000,0000,0000,,Closed down. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.65,0:08:09.75,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, in the Doll Club- 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.75,0:08:12.48,Default,Kuz,0000,0000,0000,,"To wind or not to wind?" 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.48,0:08:13.93,Default,Kuz,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't run on *****? 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:14.80,Default,Kuz,0000,0000,0000,,Closed down. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.67,0:08:19.51,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Like that, there are countless clubs that got destroyed. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.83,0:08:22.97,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want us to be closed down. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.97,0:08:28.46,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we were planning on getting you into our club as one of the Superintendent's favorite men on campus... 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.46,0:08:34.82,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,...and show her footage of how much economical adversity you're in. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:36.63,Default,3,0000,0000,0000,,And yet... 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.97,0:08:41.04,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think the Superintendent would have enjoyed watching that. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.04,0:08:46.34,Default,Kuz,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What? This was Ayasaki Hayate's embarrassing moment collection? 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.34,0:08:46.76,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.76,0:08:48.57,Default,Kuz,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see them! 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.57,0:08:50.30,Default,Kuz,0000,0000,0000,,I so wanted to see them! 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:51.31,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Kuzuha-sama. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.99,0:08:55.63,Default,Kuz,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I order the Motion Picture Research Club closed down this instant. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.02,0:09:03.76,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Starting tomorrow, start the Onono Imoko Research Club or the Eat Udon up the Nose Research Club. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.76,0:09:06.67,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Can't it be a little more normal club? 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.75,0:09:11.51,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,What a waste. We were just about to start shooting amazing footage. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.51,0:09:13.17,Default,Kuz,0000,0000,0000,,What? Amazing footage? 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.17,0:09:16.37,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,We were planning on showing it to you, too. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.42,0:09:18.57,Default,Kuz,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly will it be like? 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.19,0:09:21.76,Default,3,0000,0000,0000,,Staff credit NG collection! 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.13,0:09:23.66,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Staff credit? 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.66,0:09:26.54,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,You've seen them in Jac*** **** movies. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.54,0:09:29.71,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,In those staff credits, they play NG shots, remember? 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.71,0:09:30.77,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,That stuff. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.77,0:09:32.22,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,"That" you say, but... 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.22,0:09:33.47,Default,Kuz,0000,0000,0000,,I see. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.47,0:09:34.52,Default,Kuz,0000,0000,0000,,I do like them. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.06,0:09:37.51,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind Jac*** **** either. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.51,0:09:41.67,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my. Milady is showing interest in something that's not 2D. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.67,0:09:44.50,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,As her butler, I must do this. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:49.87,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.78,0:09:53.20,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,This is your only chance to stop. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.10,0:09:59.14,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, Hayate! 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:02.46,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,This is amazing. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.46,0:10:03.97,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,I can't miss a frame of this. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.97,0:10:05.88,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,I really think he should stop. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.45,0:10:10.60,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Ready, everyone?! 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.60,0:10:12.11,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,You will, Jac***? 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.11,0:10:13.39,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,Jump, Jac***! 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:20.87,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile... 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.86,0:10:25.64,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Makimura-san, you can't take footage like this. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.85,0:10:30.74,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,I said you can't! 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.93,0:10:36.36,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,I never imagined I'd find film this old. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.36,0:10:40.69,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,In this networked world, it's hard to recall movies that once got distributed. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.69,0:10:41.85,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.48,0:10:46.82,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Su-Sukinan dakara, mou. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.48,0:10:46.82,Note,Note,0000,0000,0000,,Su-Sukinan dakara, mou. = Y-You really like this kind of stuff. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.21,0:10:52.11,Default,3,0000,0000,0000,,Ureshinakijya, boke! 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.21,0:10:51.80,Note,Note,0000,0000,0000,,Ureshinakijya, boke! = We're crying because we're happy, you idiot! 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.11,0:10:54.93,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Hakuou Academy Motion Picture Research Club. The First... 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.12,0:10:55.80,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,...Exciting... 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:58.77,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,...Normal Story Competition! 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.33,0:11:01.71,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,What is this out of the blue? 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.71,0:11:04.71,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,What are you asking? It's obviously...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.71,0:11:05.85,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,...Just as the title reads! 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.85,0:11:08.55,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,The Motion Picture Research Club must consider safety first. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.55,0:11:13.64,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,We decided to reflect upon our acts and take footage that can be enjoyed by everyone in front of the screen. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.64,0:11:14.74,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,Yay. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.37,0:11:16.36,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.36,0:11:19.01,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you say you're leaving after coming this far. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:22.44,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,We already have a contract with the Superintendent that\Nif we present her with funny footage featuring Hayata-kun,  
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.44,0:11:26.58,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,then she'll give us 30% more funding next term. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:27.30,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,When did you do that? 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:32.35,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, Nagi-chan agreed to help as a club member. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.49,0:11:34.91,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.91,0:11:38.15,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, what is this Normal Story Competition? 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.15,0:11:40.41,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for asking, Nagi-pon. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.41,0:11:42.13,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,You see, Nagi-rin...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.13,0:11:44.35,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,...This is how it goes, Nagi Springfield. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.84,0:11:48.25,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Um, can you just call me Nagi like normal? 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.25,0:11:50.15,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,This was back when I was in elementary school. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.15,0:11:50.66,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me... 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.52,0:11:54.55,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,I was at a really rundown fishing village. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.43,0:11:59.32,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,That village seemed as though time had stopped. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.32,0:12:08.96,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx98}It was pretty creepy at first, but at the inn we stayed at, a really worn out statue of Ninomiya Kinjirou stood facing the ocean. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.96,0:12:10.90,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,From what the landlady of the inn said...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.90,0:12:16.81,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,At night, that statue turns around to make sure no kids staying at this inn are staying up late. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.30,0:12:20.79,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,So you mustn't stay up too late, okay? 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.24,0:12:23.27,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I've heard those kinds of stories before. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.27,0:12:27.30,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So we're going to gather those common stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.30,0:12:28.67,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,No! 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.67,0:12:30.36,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,The story continues. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.97,0:12:34.19,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,When you hear something like that, you have to confirm it, right? 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.17,0:12:38.82,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,At night, we snuck out with a few kids to check. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.21,0:12:41.62,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,The time was 2 AM. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.62,0:12:44.88,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,Looking back, we really shouldn't have. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.13,0:12:46.83,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,It was pitch dark out. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.83,0:12:51.72,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,It was a windy night, too, with a sound like human groaning. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.35,0:12:54.34,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,We waited for ten minutes, then twenty minutes. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.89,0:12:56.92,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,It was summer, yet it was strangely chilly. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:13:01.13,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,The next moment, we couldn't believe what we saw! 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.97,0:13:06.49,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,We had all fallen asleep at some point, and morning had come. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.49,0:13:08.90,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever happened to the statue of Kinjirou? 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.90,0:13:12.48,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone was asleep, so no one confirmed it. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.60,0:13:16.90,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,You used seventeen cuts for that worthless story?! 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.90,0:13:22.54,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,Just like that we collect normal stories where nothing happens that can't be used in any kind of context... 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.54,0:13:27.56,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,...and want to make a collection of footage that makes viewers feel, "Ah, that was a waste of time." 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.42,0:13:30.42,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need a collection like that. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:36.52,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,However, all humans have one or two worthless stories like that. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.16,0:13:40.48,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. I know you have one, too. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:43.13,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,A really worthless story that you have sealed away. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.13,0:13:44.59,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Well. Um, I... 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.31,0:13:51.25,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I used to live in a really crappy house as a kid. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.76,0:13:52.98,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,You do have one to share? 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:56.19,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,That house was really crappy. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.19,0:13:59.72,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,At night, the windows would always rattle. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.09,0:14:03.66,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,One night, I was staying at home alone. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.66,0:14:06.82,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,At the time, we didn't have electricity, so it was pitch dark inside. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.66,0:14:09.88,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to go to bed, curled up in my futon, 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.88,0:14:11.53,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,but I realized something. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.94,0:14:16.13,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,"Hey, the rattling noise is louder than usual." 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.82,0:14:22.95,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I was scared, but as though I was drawn by something, I walked towards the window. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.69,0:14:28.27,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I slowly opened the curtain,\Nand took a look outside the window, 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:30.05,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,and I noticed that... 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.05,0:14:32.16,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,...the wind was stronger than usual. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.39,0:14:36.39,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,So what?! 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.39,0:14:37.89,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing happened. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:41.19,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,But that's exactly what we're looking for. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.19,0:14:43.22,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, Hayata-kun. You know how things go. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.22,0:14:45.23,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.23,0:14:48.54,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes, yes! I want to tell my story, too! 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.54,0:14:51.22,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Katsura-sensei! Where did you come from? 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.64,0:14:56.54,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,At noon, I leave the POD room, right? 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.99,0:15:01.50,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,One day after work, I felt this\Nthe moment I stepped into the room: 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.95,0:15:03.75,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,"Something's not right." 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.23,0:15:06.34,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,At first glance, the room hadn't changed. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:11.22,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,But I could tell that something important was gone. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.24,0:15:14.49,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,I thoroughly checked the room. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.04,0:15:19.68,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Then I finally realized what I was missing. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.34,0:15:21.13,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,I was missing... 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.13,0:15:22.05,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Missing what? 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.05,0:15:24.04,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,...cash from my wallet! 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.51,0:15:28.14,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck was that?! 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.14,0:15:32.15,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I'm 500,000,000% sure it's because you used it all. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.15,0:15:33.44,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where's the mike? 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.44,0:15:37.49,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,If I may, can you listen to my story, as well? 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.49,0:15:38.62,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Klaus-san? 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.62,0:15:39.92,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,This is school, you know? 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.80,0:15:44.46,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,At this point, I'll enter any possible scenes given the opportunity. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.46,0:15:45.05,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,So. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.98,0:15:51.26,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,At the Sanzenin's, we used to have a dog named Lucky out in the yard. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.78,0:15:54.86,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, we did have a dumb dog like that, didn't we? 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.86,0:16:01.26,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,He was indeed a dumb dog, but by around six in the evening, he'd always be back and be sleeping in his place. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.26,0:16:05.05,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,But one day, he didn't come back even after the sun was starting to set. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.05,0:16:07.90,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't have him on a leash,\Nbut it didn't look like he had left the premises. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:12.40,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,But, no matter how dumb he's been, it was hard to think that he could get lost in his own yard. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.40,0:16:14.93,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,I searched for Lucky the entire night. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.93,0:16:17.89,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,But I couldn't find him, and a day passed. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.03,0:16:20.68,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,A second day went by, as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.16,0:16:24.81,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,...but Lucky wouldn't come back. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.81,0:16:26.46,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,However, on the third day! 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.76,0:16:30.38,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky was back in his home! 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.08,0:16:32.47,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why? 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.84,0:16:36.67,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,That was the end of this story. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:40.92,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for being a good audience. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.92,0:16:43.97,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,What happened during Lucky's three days? 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.76,0:16:45.75,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't know. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.75,0:16:46.76,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,Push. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.06,0:16:50.36,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,Can I tell my story, too? 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.99,0:16:56.26,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,When we were cleaning our house,\NKotetsu-kun found a really old wooden box. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:17:01.15,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,Inside the box was a mummified Kappa's hand. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.58,0:17:04.80,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,And on the inside back of the box was some scripture. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.80,0:17:08.24,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,It said that this hand will grant any three wishes of the owner. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.87,0:17:11.20,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,So, did you make your wishes? 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.20,0:17:14.27,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,No, I bet there was a fearsome curse instead. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.27,0:17:16.06,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you see... 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.06,0:17:17.23,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,We ended up... 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.23,0:17:19.38,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,...tossing it out as noncombustible trash the next day. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.36,0:17:22.92,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wouldn't a Kappa's hand be combustible? 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.92,0:17:24.79,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,She's right. It's combustible. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.79,0:17:27.23,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it is? Oopsies. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.20,0:17:30.70,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,It's now become a story about trash... 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.46,0:17:33.26,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Right, I'm up next. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.54,0:17:37.00,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Do you all know the word "doppelganger"? 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.55,0:17:41.71,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,It's about meeting an individual who's like a copy of yourself. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:46.78,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,It's said whoever sees a doppelganger will soon die after that. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.02,0:17:50.20,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,It's said that Lincoln saw one the day before he was assassinated, too. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.20,0:17:54.43,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,A Japanese poet, Murou Saisei, also saw a doppelganger. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.43,0:17:56.65,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,This time, it's starting to sound like an urban legend. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.82,0:18:03.70,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't the name Murou Saisei sound just like Slow Saisei? 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.82,0:18:03.70,Note,Note,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Slow Saisei = The slow play setting on video players
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.06,0:18:10.17,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Also, toudai motogurashi and\Ntaishou democracy sounds similar, too. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.17,0:18:13.85,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, Jura*** Park and Ju**ke ni nisanpaku sounds similar, too. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.57,0:18:14.94,Default-alt,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Those really are things no one cares about. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.59,0:18:18.77,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,It's all up to you to believe it or not. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.77,0:18:19.91,Default,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,Um... 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.22,0:18:24.89,Default,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,May I share my story from home? 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.89,0:18:25.94,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Saki-san. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.64,0:18:32.09,Default,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,My home is really old, and whenever someone uses the stairwell, it makes creaking noises. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.06,0:18:39.58,Default,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,One day, the whole family was eating on the first floor, but we heard the creaking noise from the stairs. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.96,0:18:45.37,Default,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,So Mom said, "Wow, our house must really be getting old", and so we renovated. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.37,0:18:47.55,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,That really was a normal story. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.93,0:18:53.03,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,My god. Those were all really boring stories. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.03,0:18:54.07,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru-kun? 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.07,0:18:56.18,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, if it isn't him; you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.18,0:18:57.85,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,President! Our club president! 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.13,0:18:59.09,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,President? 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.09,0:19:00.60,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, that's right. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.60,0:19:04.09,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,The boy standing there is the current\NMotion Picture Research Club's president,  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.09,0:19:06.64,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Tachibana Wataru-kun! 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.64,0:19:08.18,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Tada. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.18,0:19:10.55,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,You just forced me to be the president. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.05,0:19:12.33,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,When did this happen? 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.32,0:19:15.28,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know, the president's amazing. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.28,0:19:20.00,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,He makes MAD anime openings that could fool the eyes of people who don't watch anime. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.28,0:19:19.97,Note,Note,0000,0000,0000,,Note: A MAD movie is a Japanese fan-made video, much like AMVs (Anime Music Videos) 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.00,0:19:23.52,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Also, all the OreVoice series are made by him! 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.49,0:19:26.46,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,No, they're making that up. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.46,0:19:30.62,Default,Wik,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, come on. None of them have any punch lines. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.62,0:19:32.30,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,As expected of our President. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.30,0:19:36.64,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Then what, you can tell a story with a punch line? 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.64,0:19:37.39,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.83,0:19:42.29,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,But what I'm saying is, I want to hear a more touching normal story that strikes one's heart. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.58,0:19:45.84,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,"A normal story that strikes one's heart?" 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.84,0:19:47.59,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, for example. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.59,0:19:49.17,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,This is regarding outer space. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.27,0:19:53.51,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,You know how space is expanding at great speed, right? 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.51,0:19:54.57,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.69,0:20:00.23,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Also, you know that light is the fastest thing in the universe, right? 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.23,0:20:02.03,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Well, since it's common sense. 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.03,0:20:06.52,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,However, the rate of expansion is greater the further you are from Earth. 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.08,0:20:11.98,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, the stars further away from Earth will distance themselves from Earth more quickly,  
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.80,0:20:17.50,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,and eventually, they will go past the speed of light! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.13,0:20:20.30,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.84,0:20:24.66,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,It's a mystery, isn't it? 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.15,0:20:27.46,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,P-President... 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.46,0:20:29.51,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,Was that the end? 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.90,0:20:35.48,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,So that ends one worthless day. 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.89,0:20:41.59,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if anything good happens. 
